Body:
Description: Hello,

In your ticketing platform is missing latest Server Version. Ticketing is 5.9.4.0, server version is 5.9.4.1.

You should update this section.

Thanks

What We've Learned Updated: Client reported to us that currently, on the netwrix support portal, we are still using 5.9.4.0 version instead of 5.9.4.1 and he is wondering when we will update the portal.
Next Steps Updated: Will have to update the client that we are aware of it and our team is working on this update implementation.
